      "span_text": "Follow-up within-group t tests yielded a significantly greater caudate response for interest reward than social Given the nonselective nature of this analysis  , we additionally investigated unbiased individual β values averaged across an anatomically defined bilateral caudate mask (based on the Harvard-Oxford probabilistic atlas).",
